Events.Text: I need directions from University to Airport at 6pm by driving

Scenario.UserTask: You want directions from 'University' to 'Airport' at 6 pm by Driving. When the wizard gives the 1st and 4th step, indicate that you do not understand until you are given more detail. Keep going until you've reached your destination.
Scenario.WizardTask: Tell the user the directions from their departure location to their arrival location
